Description: replace embedded mikmod with libopenmpt for XM playback
 Replace the old embedded libmikmod (SDL1 callback-based) with libopenmpt,
 which provides accurate XM playback and exposes pattern/row position
 via openmpt_module_get_current_order/row, preserving music synchronisation.
 SDL_OpenAudioDevice (SDL2) is used instead of the deprecated SDL_OpenAudio.
 Also remove SDL_INIT_NOPARACHUTE (dropped in SDL2) and add SDL_INIT_AUDIO.
Generated-by: Claude Sonnet 4.6
Reviewed-by: Nicolas HOUDELOT <nicolas@demosdebs.org>
Applied-Upstream: no
